node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Apple Hub on August 12, 2021. May be an image of phone and text that says 'iPhone 120 TrendForce TrendForceoutlinesxpc outlines expectations 5nm A15 Chip mmWave 5G in more countries Larger batteries Same prices expected September launch @theapplehub'.

node.text:
Taiwanese research firm TrendForce has outlined some of their expectation for the upcoming iPhone models. One month to go!

#Apple #iPhone12s #iPhone13 #Tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Apple Hub on August 10, 2021 tagging @silicondesigner. May be an image of phone and text that says 'iPhone 12 129 S expected features Portrait Mode for video ProRes for videos Smaller notch Advanced filters using AI A15 Chip 120Hz ProMotion Always- display @theapplehub Render from @silicondesigner'.

node.text:
According to Bloomberg’s Mark Gurman, the upcoming iPhone models will feature more advanced camera features including ProRes for videos (likely exclusive to the Pro models) and Portrait Mode for video. The upcoming iPhone models are expected to launch next month.

#Apple #iPhone12s #iPhone13 #Tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Apple Hub on August 10, 2021. May be an image of laptop, screen and text that says 'MacBook Pro with OLED display coming in 2022 @theapplehub Modified image from Apple'.

node.text:
According to The Elec, future MacBook Pro models will feature OLED displays and Samsung Display has begun development of a new production process for OLED displays that will be used by Apple for the MacBook Pro.

#Apple #MacBook #MacBookPro #Tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Apple Hub on August 10, 2021 tagging @rendersbyian. May be an image of text that says 'MacBook Air with Mini-LED display launching in Mid 2022 R RENDERSETIAN PROSSER RENDERS @theapplehub Render from @rendersbyian'.

node.text:
According to analyst Ming-Chi Kuo, Apple plans to launch a new MacBook Air with a Mini-LED display and multiple color options in mid 2022. The new Air will feature a new design similar to the MacBook Pro design. Render from @rendersbyian

#Apple #MacBook #MacBookAir #Tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Apple Hub on August 06, 2021. May be an image of phone, screen and text.

node.text:
Apple has announced that starting with iOS 15 and iPadOS 15, Apple will be able to detect child sexual abuse material images in user’s libraries and report them to the National Center for Missing and Exploited Children (NCMEC). This would only work for images stored in iCloud Photos.

#Apple #iOS15 #iPhone12 #Tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Apple Hub on August 05, 2021 tagging @rendersbyian. May be an image of phone, wrist watch and text that says 'New Products coming next month NewYork @theapplehub Vatch render @rendersbyian'.

node.text:
Apple is expected to launch new products next month including new iPhone and Apple Watch models. Which upcoming products are you most excited about? Apple Watch render from @rendersbyian 

#Apple #iPhone12s #iPhone13 #AppleWatch #Tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Apple Hub on August 03, 2021 tagging @rendersbyian. May be an image of screen, wrist watch and text.

node.text:
New, unreleased Apple product filings have been discovered in the Eurasian Economic Commission database. The listings are for new Macs (presumably the upcoming MacBook Pro models) and new Apple Watch models. Apple is expected to launch new products next month. Render from @rendersbyian 

#Apple #Mac #MacBookPro #AppleWatch #Tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Apple Hub on July 26, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'iPhone 14 14Pro to feature titanium alloy chassis @theapplehub Apple'.

node.text:
According to an investors report by JP Morgan Chase, next year’s Pro iPhone models will feature a titanium alloy chassis design. They expect next year to be an iPhone‌ supercycle year, a year many people upgrade to the latest model.

#Apple #iPhone13 #iPhone14 #iPhone14Pro #Tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Apple Hub on July 26, 2021 tagging @rendersbyian. May be an image of phone, screen and text.

node.text:
According to display analyst Ross Young, the upcoming iPad mini will feature an 8.3” display due to narrower bezels and the removal of the Home Button. Render from @rendersbyian

#Apple #iPad #iPadmini #Tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Apple Hub on July 24, 2021. May be an image of screen, television and text that says 'External Display with A13 Chip in the works @theapplehub Apple'.

node.text:
According to 9to5Mac, Apple is internally testing a new external display with a built-in A13 Bionic Chip and a Neural Engine. This new display could replace the Pro Display XDR in the future.

#Apple #Mac #ProDisplayXDR #Display #tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Apple Hub on July 24, 2021. May be an image of phone and text that says 'iPhone 12日 may support 25W fast charging 11 @theapplehub Apple'.

node.text:
A post on Chinese website MyDrivers claims the upcoming iPhone models may support fast charging up to 25W. The current iPhone 12 lineup supports fast charging up to 20W.

#Apple #iPhone12s #iPhone13 #tech #AppleHub

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Apple Hub on July 23, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'iPhone 129Pro 12 Pro new colors @theapplehub'.

node.text:
An alleged supply chain leak posted on a Korean-language message board by Ranzuk claims the new Pro iPhone models will be available in Black, Silver, Rose Gold, and Sunset Gold. Which color would you get?

#Apple #iPhone12s #iPhone13 #tech #AppleHub
